'''Drax''' was the [[Captain/Legends|captain]] of the Imperial transport ship ''[[High Hauler]]''. In a cover story, [[Alfonso Luiz Obota]] pretended to be [[Alfonso Luiz Obota|Hortu Agar]]&mdash;the ship's engineering officer&mdash;and cited Drax's death as the reason he assumed command of the vessel.

